column4: X: 1=Left most column, counting to the right to max of 2 or 3
column5: Y: 1 equals top row (i.e., out of play heavenly bead), counting downwards to 7.
column6: Correct on Search task? Trials weith incorrect search responses were excluded from analysis

column12: <3Std Dev: removing outliers (2s). Calculated in linear space. Needs to be redone in log space
